turn-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8419089\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104blo1665702710364_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/blo1665702710364_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/blo1665702710364_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"blo1665702710364\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Wide Character Behavior\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the character set used for String fields with the W packing code. If the database does not support Unicode, or it supports only Unicode BMP, use this setting to change its behavior. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">Unicode</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">BMP</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Use Character Set</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"blo1665702710364__section_w1911ab1b5b1_w1912ab1b5_w1913ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">(default)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__2\">Default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Unicode</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Unicode</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__2\">Full range of Unicode character set (Default). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">BMP</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__2\">\n Basic Multilingual Plane. Unicode character set ranging from 0000 to FFFF.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Use Character Set</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"blo1665702710364__table_d626e1_d627e1_d628e1__entry__2\">Switches the <code class=\"ph codeph\">W</code> packing code to\n                        the <code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code> packing code. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"blo1665702710364__section_g4l_q1h_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d219703e157\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"blo1665702710364__p_d7229e1_d7230e1_d7231e1\">If you set this property to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Use Character\n               Set</code>, you must also set the value of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Character Set</span>\n            property or the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DEF_CHARSET</span> assignment setting.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"blo1665702710364__p_d7232e1_d7233e1_d7234e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Wide Character Behavior</span>\n            property overrides the value given by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR</span>\n            assignment setting.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"blo1665702710364__section_a1p_r1h_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d219703e184\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"blo1665702710364__ul_zkh_t1h_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"blo1665702710364__li_d3584e1_d3585e1_d3586e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hzd1665702710226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzd1665702710226.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity.\">Modeled Entity Interface</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uir1665702875362.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Packing Codes for Unicode</a><p>By default, the W packing code is for Unicode characters. The U* packing code can also be used for holding Unicode characters. If the entity character set is Unicode, the C packing code can also be used for Unicode characters.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udi1665702731005.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Unicode</a><p>Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udr1665702710295.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Character Set</a><p>Character set used for storing the entity in the database.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wzv1665702719081.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR</a><p>Specify the character set used for String fields with the W packing code.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419089\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419089\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Wide Character Behavior Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Wide Character Behavior Specify the character set used for String fields with the W packing code. If the database does not support Unicode, or it supports only Unicode BMP, use this setting to change its behavior. Valid values are Unicode , BMP , or Use Character Set . Value Description (default) Default is Unicode . Unicode Full range of Unicode character set (Default). BMP Basic Multilingual Plane. Unicode character set ranging from 0000 to FFFF. Use Character Set Switches the W packing code to the C packing code. Description If you set this property to Use Character Set , you must also set the value of the Character Set property or the $DEF_CHARSET assignment setting. The Wide Character Behavior property overrides the value given by the $WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR assignment setting. Applies To Modeled Entity Interface Related Links Packing Codes for Unicode By default, the W packing code is for Unicode characters. The U* packing code can also be used for holding Unicode characters. If the entity character set is Unicode, the C packing code can also be used for Unicode characters. Unicode Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers. Character Set Character set used for storing the entity in the database. $WIDE_CHAR_BEHAVIOR Specify the character set used for String fields with the W packing code. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}